1
00:00:49,280 --> 00:00:53,000
[The Ferry Man: 10th Anniversary]

2
00:00:53,440 --> 00:00:56,060
[Episode 3]

3
00:00:59,670 --> 00:01:00,870
There are only 2 of us.

4
00:01:02,150 --> 00:01:02,750
Besides,

5
00:01:03,150 --> 00:01:05,209
I thought you didn't know how to play.

6
00:01:06,200 --> 00:01:06,730
Let's go.

7
00:01:07,070 --> 00:01:08,470
Let's go play over there.

8
00:01:08,510 --> 00:01:10,510
Are we really playing? It's so late.

9
00:01:11,120 --> 00:01:11,640
Come on.

10
00:01:12,120 --> 00:01:12,950
Come on, let's go.

11
00:01:12,950 --> 00:01:14,150
Let's start playing.

12
00:01:21,590 --> 00:01:23,050
Can I play basketball now?

13
00:01:35,789 --> 00:01:36,990
I can lend you my body.

14
00:01:37,940 --> 00:01:39,430
Mom doesn't like me playing basketball.

15
00:01:39,430 --> 00:01:41,090
She hasn't even seen you play.

16
00:01:41,120 --> 00:01:41,870
How would she know

17
00:01:41,870 --> 00:01:42,800
how good you are?

18
00:01:49,070 --> 00:01:49,560
Come on.

19
00:01:50,509 --> 00:01:51,000
You

20
00:01:51,710 --> 00:01:53,259
play better than all of them.

21
00:01:53,259 --> 00:01:54,400
Show your mom

22
00:01:54,430 --> 00:01:55,690
how excellent you are.

23
00:01:56,840 --> 00:01:58,440
Your shot's pretty on point.

24
00:01:58,479 --> 00:01:59,870
Looks like I'll need to mark you
more closely.

25
00:01:59,870 --> 00:02:01,070
Nice three-pointer.

26
00:02:10,030 --> 00:02:11,430
Come on, pass me the ball.

27
00:02:12,630 --> 00:02:13,830
Pass it to me. Come on.

28
00:02:38,030 --> 00:02:39,230
Guard him! Over here!

29
00:02:39,240 --> 00:02:39,840
Guard him!

30
00:02:40,240 --> 00:02:42,100
It's okay. Focus on the next play.

31
00:02:50,850 --> 00:02:52,310
I can't stop him by myself.

32
00:02:52,590 --> 00:02:53,390
Help defense!

33
00:02:58,829 --> 00:03:00,030
It's okay. It's okay.

34
00:03:02,010 --> 00:03:03,210
Block him! Block him!

35
00:03:06,310 --> 00:03:07,240
So accurate.

36
00:03:07,800 --> 00:03:09,400
I think I saw my son.

37
00:03:58,800 --> 00:03:59,400
Mom.

38
00:04:00,150 --> 00:04:01,310
This is my dream.

39
00:04:11,120 --> 00:04:12,320
The words on the desk,

40
00:04:13,430 --> 00:04:15,560
the wind through the basketball hoop—

41
00:04:15,840 --> 00:04:17,920
only after life and death
stood between them

42
00:04:17,920 --> 00:04:19,519
did she finally see clearly.

43
00:04:20,480 --> 00:04:23,150
With the smile of someone
who had been truly understood,

44
00:04:23,150 --> 00:04:25,350
he crossed the River of Forgetfulness.

45
00:04:26,720 --> 00:04:27,680
Some regrets

46
00:04:29,040 --> 00:04:31,820
refuse to settle
until the soul has grown light enough

47
00:04:31,820 --> 00:04:32,750
to let them go.

48
00:04:36,810 --> 00:04:40,370
[Chapter 3: Guhuo Bird]

49
00:04:48,720 --> 00:04:49,510
Honey.

50
00:04:49,870 --> 00:04:50,620
Can you stop listening to

51
00:04:50,620 --> 00:04:51,550
horror stories?

52
00:04:53,070 --> 00:04:55,000
It's my only hobby.

53
00:04:56,560 --> 00:04:59,220
Well, at least think about
prenatal education.

54
00:05:04,040 --> 00:05:06,700
What kind of pregnant woman
still wears makeup?

55
00:05:07,480 --> 00:05:09,510
I'm just trying to
brighten up my complexion a bit.

56
00:05:09,510 --> 00:05:10,430
So naggy.

57
00:05:11,510 --> 00:05:13,440
You never listen to anything I say.

58
00:05:15,920 --> 00:05:18,950
♪ One dies, two live ♪

59
00:05:19,420 --> 00:05:22,420
♪ Three together live happily ever after ♪

60
00:05:22,630 --> 00:05:24,480
-What are you singing?
-♪ One dies ♪

61
00:05:24,480 --> 00:05:25,720
Wait, what are you singing?

62
00:05:25,720 --> 00:05:27,050
A horror nursery rhyme.

63
00:05:27,160 --> 00:05:28,600
If you keep nagging me, I'll use this

64
00:05:28,600 --> 00:05:29,730
to educate your son.

65
00:05:29,920 --> 00:05:31,560
Cut it out. It's bad luck.

66
00:05:32,680 --> 00:05:34,800
♪ One dies, two live ♪

67
00:05:34,830 --> 00:05:37,690
♪ Three together live happily ever after ♪

68
00:05:36,830 --> 00:05:38,159
Can't you stop singing?

69
00:05:45,800 --> 00:05:46,400
Luo Hao...

70
00:05:47,800 --> 00:05:49,000
What's wrong, Honey?

71
00:05:49,390 --> 00:05:50,430
My belly hurts.

72
00:05:51,000 --> 00:05:51,920
Is it the baby?

73
00:05:54,940 --> 00:05:55,770
What's wrong?

74
00:05:59,070 --> 00:05:59,830
Luo Hao!

75
00:06:00,920 --> 00:06:01,600
Hurry!

76
00:06:02,070 --> 00:06:03,160
To the hospital...

77
00:06:03,390 --> 00:06:03,950
Okay.

78
00:06:04,390 --> 00:06:04,870
Okay!

79
00:06:05,390 --> 00:06:06,590
Hang in there, Honey!

80
00:06:14,750 --> 00:06:15,360
Li.

81
00:06:15,720 --> 00:06:16,830
I've got an important guest.

82
00:06:16,830 --> 00:06:17,920
Don't let anyone in the back room.

83
00:06:17,920 --> 00:06:18,250
Okay.

84
00:06:23,360 --> 00:06:24,160
Welcom...

85
00:06:31,360 --> 00:06:32,690
Your Majesty the Queen.

86
00:06:32,870 --> 00:06:33,390
Please.

87
00:07:04,750 --> 00:07:06,830
I'm back, Heavenly Maiden.

88
00:07:07,430 --> 00:07:08,430
Yan Yuzhen?

89
00:07:12,040 --> 00:07:13,750
Born from imagination,

90
00:07:14,240 --> 00:07:15,950
carried on people's lips.

91
00:07:16,720 --> 00:07:18,720
Desire never dies—

92
00:07:19,630 --> 00:07:21,230
it renews itself endlessly.

93
00:07:24,120 --> 00:07:24,890
Yan Yuzhen,

94
00:07:25,120 --> 00:07:26,050
it really is you.

95
00:07:26,270 --> 00:07:27,510
It's the eternal queen,

96
00:07:27,510 --> 00:07:28,510
Lady Yan Yuzhen.

97
00:07:29,240 --> 00:07:30,000
I said

98
00:07:30,560 --> 00:07:31,510
I'd come back.

99
00:07:46,040 --> 00:07:47,680
You've changed a bit.

100
00:07:48,040 --> 00:07:49,270
Well, I've had a little work done

101
00:07:49,270 --> 00:07:50,360
on this face.

102
00:07:50,950 --> 00:07:52,690
More than just a little, I'd say.

103
00:07:52,690 --> 00:07:54,040
This face is more fashionable

104
00:07:54,040 --> 00:07:56,040
and fits the current trends better.

105
00:08:02,600 --> 00:08:03,360
I know

106
00:08:03,920 --> 00:08:05,680
that you married Xia Dongqing

107
00:08:08,480 --> 00:08:10,120
and opened this café.

108
00:08:16,040 --> 00:08:17,720
Are you really okay with

109
00:08:19,360 --> 00:08:21,160
living an ordinary life for him?

110
00:08:22,160 --> 00:08:23,360
I've got work to do,

111
00:08:23,560 --> 00:08:24,960
and I'm pretty good at it.

112
00:08:27,390 --> 00:08:28,450
It's been 10 years.

113
00:08:29,480 --> 00:08:32,080
Dongqing was just a college student
back then.

114
00:08:32,080 --> 00:08:34,150
He was so young.

115
00:08:54,960 --> 00:08:56,150
What are your real intentions

116
00:08:56,150 --> 00:08:57,210
in coming to see me?

117
00:09:00,240 --> 00:09:01,500
To cooperate with you.

118
00:09:02,480 --> 00:09:03,270
Don't worry.

119
00:09:03,510 --> 00:09:05,040
I've turned over a new leaf.

120
00:09:06,390 --> 00:09:08,000
Seducing men one by one

121
00:09:08,030 --> 00:09:09,600
and feeding on their life essence

122
00:09:09,600 --> 00:09:10,840
was just too exhausting

123
00:09:10,840 --> 00:09:11,840
and inefficient.

124
00:09:12,870 --> 00:09:14,600
I want to become an influencer—

125
00:09:14,630 --> 00:09:15,720
a top-tier one.

126
00:09:16,230 --> 00:09:17,550
Once I've built my following,

127
00:09:17,550 --> 00:09:19,810
I'll expand the brand and monetize my IP.

128
00:09:20,240 --> 00:09:21,370
When the time comes,

129
00:09:21,390 --> 00:09:23,330
I'll turn the name "Yan Yuzhen"

130
00:09:23,480 --> 00:09:25,550
into a global IP franchise.

131
00:09:26,720 --> 00:09:28,320
You want to be an influencer?

132
00:09:29,480 --> 00:09:30,280
Don't forget,

133
00:09:30,910 --> 00:09:32,200
I've always been very popular

134
00:09:32,200 --> 00:09:33,860
throughout Chinese history.

135
00:09:33,860 --> 00:09:34,600
I'm basically

136
00:09:34,600 --> 00:09:35,840
a top-tier IP myself.

137
00:09:36,390 --> 00:09:37,790
I just don't understand.

138
00:09:38,790 --> 00:09:40,550
Why do you want to be an influencer?

139
00:09:40,550 --> 00:09:41,120
Oh, you.

140
00:09:41,390 --> 00:09:42,550
Don't overthink it.

141
00:09:43,200 --> 00:09:45,530
Beauty like mine is just born to
stand out.

142
00:09:46,000 --> 00:09:47,200
Throughout history,

143
00:09:47,510 --> 00:09:49,910
beauty has always been a marketable asset.

144
00:09:51,080 --> 00:09:52,600
Back in my time,

145
00:09:52,850 --> 00:09:53,840
if a woman

146
00:09:53,870 --> 00:09:56,240
wanted to climb the social ladder
with her looks,

147
00:09:56,240 --> 00:09:58,300
she had no choice but to depend on men.

148
00:09:59,480 --> 00:10:01,910
Even an emperor wasn't reliable.

149
00:10:03,480 --> 00:10:05,140
But things are different now.

150
00:10:05,480 --> 00:10:06,610
I'm this beautiful,

151
00:10:06,790 --> 00:10:08,450
so why wouldn't I monetize it?

152
00:10:47,870 --> 00:10:49,000
Hello. What can I...

153
00:10:49,360 --> 00:10:51,160
Isn't this a convenience store?

154
00:10:51,360 --> 00:10:52,620
We're actually a café,

155
00:10:52,720 --> 00:10:54,120
just named "Convenience Store."

156
00:10:54,120 --> 00:10:55,480
You know, our boss might be a bit...

157
00:10:55,480 --> 00:10:56,610
Do you have any food?

158
00:10:56,630 --> 00:10:57,000
Yes.

159
00:10:57,120 --> 00:10:57,750
We have cakes,

160
00:10:57,750 --> 00:10:58,390
pasta,

161
00:10:58,550 --> 00:10:59,150
and steak.

162
00:10:59,200 --> 00:11:00,130
What do you want?

163
00:11:03,030 --> 00:11:04,490
It must be very expensive.

164
00:11:23,960 --> 00:11:24,890
Did you see that?

165
00:11:25,150 --> 00:11:26,150
Not very clearly.

166
00:11:26,670 --> 00:11:28,070
But something feels off.

167
00:11:29,490 --> 00:11:31,020
I need to go to the café first

168
00:11:31,200 --> 00:11:32,240
to handle a few things.

169
00:11:32,240 --> 00:11:32,690
Alright.

170
00:11:32,690 --> 00:11:34,620
Then I'll go check what's going on.

171
00:11:45,440 --> 00:11:45,840
Li,

172
00:11:46,120 --> 00:11:47,050
where's my wife?

173
00:11:47,840 --> 00:11:48,720
She's inside.

174
00:11:50,480 --> 00:11:51,740
Boss, Boss. Come here.

175
00:11:53,790 --> 00:11:54,320
There's a

176
00:11:54,320 --> 00:11:55,910
super beautiful woman inside.

177
00:11:55,910 --> 00:11:56,970
A beautiful woman?

178
00:11:58,240 --> 00:11:59,670
Even more beautiful than my wife?

179
00:11:59,670 --> 00:12:01,070
She totally crushed her.

180
00:12:01,600 --> 00:12:02,360
Then I must have

181
00:12:02,360 --> 00:12:03,080
a good look.

182
00:12:25,150 --> 00:12:26,100
H-Hello,

183
00:12:27,000 --> 00:12:28,320
I'm the boss here.

184
00:12:29,440 --> 00:12:30,030
Sanlang.

185
00:12:31,630 --> 00:12:32,270
Sanlang.

186
00:12:32,840 --> 00:12:33,630
Sanlang!

187
00:12:34,320 --> 00:12:35,480
I missed you so much.

188
00:12:38,080 --> 00:12:39,550
Miss.

189
00:12:39,720 --> 00:12:40,550
Lady.

190
00:12:41,130 --> 00:12:42,000
It's improper for men and women
to have physical contact.

191
00:12:42,000 --> 00:12:43,000
Really improper.

192
00:12:43,510 --> 00:12:44,240
Sanlang,

193
00:12:44,910 --> 00:12:46,320
I'm Yuzhen.

194
00:12:51,550 --> 00:12:52,270
How about

195
00:12:52,600 --> 00:12:54,330
we get to know each other again?

196
00:13:00,750 --> 00:13:01,950
You shameless vixen!

197
00:13:05,150 --> 00:13:05,600
You...

198
00:13:06,120 --> 00:13:07,050
Let go of my wife!

199
00:13:20,600 --> 00:13:21,720
We're all old acquaintances.

200
00:13:21,720 --> 00:13:23,050
What's that fuss about?

201
00:13:30,360 --> 00:13:32,510
"Flying into a rage for a beauty"—

202
00:13:32,670 --> 00:13:34,550
that's not my poem.

203
00:13:34,780 --> 00:13:36,120
If the customers outside hear this,

204
00:13:36,120 --> 00:13:37,180
that'd be awkward.

205
00:13:44,960 --> 00:13:46,160
Come on, let's drink.

206
00:13:46,630 --> 00:13:47,480
Bottoms up.

207
00:13:51,510 --> 00:13:52,970
Beautiful, are you alone?

208
00:13:53,840 --> 00:13:55,370
Come over and drink with us.

209
00:13:57,270 --> 00:13:59,330
Let's drink. Getting shy, isn't she?

210
00:14:09,080 --> 00:14:09,910
ID card.

211
00:14:21,550 --> 00:14:22,320
The deposit

212
00:14:22,600 --> 00:14:23,270
is 200 yuan.

213
00:15:09,480 --> 00:15:10,670
Hot water for bathing

214
00:15:10,670 --> 00:15:12,120
is available from 8 a.m. to 8 p.m.

215
00:15:12,120 --> 00:15:13,720
There's an electric kettle in the room.

216
00:15:13,720 --> 00:15:14,780
Boil your own water

217
00:15:15,240 --> 00:15:16,040
if you need it.

218
00:15:47,410 --> 00:15:49,180
[Golden Pages ]

219
00:16:14,150 --> 00:16:14,750
Hello.

220
00:16:15,200 --> 00:16:16,600
Do you need room service?

221
00:16:16,670 --> 00:16:17,630
Are you crazy?

222
00:16:50,950 --> 00:16:52,790
[Mom]

223
00:16:56,480 --> 00:16:57,200
Mom.

224
00:17:01,790 --> 00:17:02,670
I'm okay.

225
00:17:06,400 --> 00:17:08,349
I can't tell you where I am.

226
00:17:09,109 --> 00:17:10,550
I can't say it!

227
00:17:11,839 --> 00:17:12,839
If I tell you,

228
00:17:13,550 --> 00:17:15,270
Luo Hao will find me.

229
00:17:17,000 --> 00:17:18,640
He'll come to hurt us.

230
00:17:20,030 --> 00:17:21,200
He wants me and the baby

231
00:17:21,200 --> 00:17:22,680
to go to hell together with him!

232
00:17:22,680 --> 00:17:23,640
I'm not crazy!

233
00:17:24,099 --> 00:17:26,829
Everything I said is true, Mom.

234
00:17:36,750 --> 00:17:37,480
Mom.

235
00:17:37,920 --> 00:17:39,440
Watch out for mirrors.

236
00:17:43,240 --> 00:17:44,400
Ghosts

237
00:17:45,510 --> 00:17:46,960
can come through them.

238
00:18:26,960 --> 00:18:27,760
Can I help you?

239
00:18:29,090 --> 00:18:30,950
Sorry, I got the wrong room.

240
00:18:46,640 --> 00:18:48,680
♪ One dies ♪

241
00:18:49,590 --> 00:18:51,960
♪ Two live ♪

242
00:18:52,730 --> 00:18:58,120
♪ Three together live happily ever after ♪

243
00:18:52,920 --> 00:18:53,980
It's time to sleep.

244
00:18:56,110 --> 00:18:57,480
Let me put you to sleep.

245
00:19:02,030 --> 00:19:04,590
♪ One dies ♪

246
00:19:05,720 --> 00:19:08,640
♪ Two live ♪

247
00:19:09,680 --> 00:19:16,920
♪ Three together live happily ever after ♪

